  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras/7ed37fc4b41fa8a45b3ba4a81df76f8a.avif?t=1746097238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras_big/7ed37fc4b41fa8a45b3ba4a81df76f8a.avif?t=1746097238 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Xiao Wang phone store simulator a mobile phone sales and management simulation game, players through reasonable management, earn money, expand the scale of the store, open the secret room. You will become the owner of Xiao Wang's Repair Shop and expand its scale. By purchasing second-hand mobile phones, refurbishing and repairing them, you can earn gold coins. Then, you can open the mysterious chamber and explore the secrets hidden within. Unravel the secrets left by Xiao Wang.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras/ff3f646f9ab5992c5ff0bee2e6e76f49.avif?t=1746097238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras_big/ff3f646f9ab5992c5ff0bee2e6e76f49.avif?t=1746097238 width=800 height=450 /></span>You can buy a mobile phone directly on the computer or draw a blind box, make sure you have enough money before drawing the blind box, otherwise it is easy to go bankrupt.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras/07e1864d0ff900970763ddf50949d346.avif?t=1746097238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras_big/07e1864d0ff900970763ddf50949d346.avif?t=1746097238 width=800 height=450 /></span>In the blind box you have the opportunity to make a fortune on a luxury phone, but you need to fix it first.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras/72419629a751c026d6d022e452e6fc7e.avif?t=1746097238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras_big/72419629a751c026d6d022e452e6fc7e.avif?t=1746097238 width=800 height=450 /></span>If the repair fails, the phone will explode directly, and even the most luxurious mobile phone can only be sold as scrap for 50 yuan.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras/345bf70d23768d09a1e5de53181a5198.avif?t=1746097238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras_big/345bf70d23768d09a1e5de53181a5198.avif?t=1746097238 width=800 height=450 /></span>You can display your phone on a display case, which can be used to attract customers.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras/1bb65551d4811b41852b3bd52201441f.avif?t=1746097238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras_big/1bb65551d4811b41852b3bd52201441f.avif?t=1746097238 width=800 height=450 /></span>You can earn money to expand your shop, but it costs a lot of gold.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras/6aab53b95d9ec5c8bdecdcce972cba90.avif?t=1746097238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras_big/6aab53b95d9ec5c8bdecdcce972cba90.avif?t=1746097238 width=800 height=450 /></span>You can create your own wall of phone in a larger store<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras/cec1ff3ba7277dc646d4223e2f77cfc9.avif?t=1746097238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras_big/cec1ff3ba7277dc646d4223e2f77cfc9.avif?t=1746097238 width=800 height=450 /></span>There are also a lot of easter eggs hidden in the game, which can be on the street, in a store, or in a secret room, which will not prompt anything, some may have to be clicked, and some may have to wait a while to trigger.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras/7ed37fc4b41fa8a45b3ba4a81df76f8a.avif?t=1746097238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras_big/7ed37fc4b41fa8a45b3ba4a81df76f8a.avif?t=1746097238 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Xiao Wang phone store simulator a mobile phone sales and management simulation game, players through reasonable management, earn money, expand the scale of the store, open the secret room. You will become the owner of Xiao Wang's Repair Shop and expand its scale. By purchasing second-hand mobile phones, refurbishing and repairing them, you can earn gold coins. Then, you can open the mysterious chamber and explore the secrets hidden within. Unravel the secrets left by Xiao Wang.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras/ff3f646f9ab5992c5ff0bee2e6e76f49.avif?t=1746097238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras_big/ff3f646f9ab5992c5ff0bee2e6e76f49.avif?t=1746097238 width=800 height=450 /></span>You can buy a mobile phone directly on the computer or draw a blind box, make sure you have enough money before drawing the blind box, otherwise it is easy to go bankrupt.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras/07e1864d0ff900970763ddf50949d346.avif?t=1746097238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras_big/07e1864d0ff900970763ddf50949d346.avif?t=1746097238 width=800 height=450 /></span>In the blind box you have the opportunity to make a fortune on a luxury phone, but you need to fix it first.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras/72419629a751c026d6d022e452e6fc7e.avif?t=1746097238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras_big/72419629a751c026d6d022e452e6fc7e.avif?t=1746097238 width=800 height=450 /></span>If the repair fails, the phone will explode directly, and even the most luxurious mobile phone can only be sold as scrap for 50 yuan.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras/345bf70d23768d09a1e5de53181a5198.avif?t=1746097238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras_big/345bf70d23768d09a1e5de53181a5198.avif?t=1746097238 width=800 height=450 /></span>You can display your phone on a display case, which can be used to attract customers.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras/1bb65551d4811b41852b3bd52201441f.avif?t=1746097238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras_big/1bb65551d4811b41852b3bd52201441f.avif?t=1746097238 width=800 height=450 /></span>You can earn money to expand your shop, but it costs a lot of gold.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras/6aab53b95d9ec5c8bdecdcce972cba90.avif?t=1746097238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras_big/6aab53b95d9ec5c8bdecdcce972cba90.avif?t=1746097238 width=800 height=450 /></span>You can create your own wall of phone in a larger store<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras/cec1ff3ba7277dc646d4223e2f77cfc9.avif?t=1746097238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3514840/extras_big/cec1ff3ba7277dc646d4223e2f77cfc9.avif?t=1746097238 width=800 height=450 /></span>There are also a lot of easter eggs hidden in the game, which can be on the street, in a store, or in a secret room, which will not prompt anything, some may have to be clicked, and some may have to wait a while to trigger.</p>",
